{
  "id": "adv_bond_ski_01_05",
  "title": "白石沙季5",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ski_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_ski_01_05-ski001.m4a",
      "text": "妹……妹とは一体……妹のいいところとは……\nやはり、心を許して甘えてくれるところ……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A younger sister… what is she‚ really? Her good points are…\nI guess‚ the way she opens up and acts spoiled…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ski_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_ski_01_05-smr001.m4a",
      "text": "ふんふんふ～ん\nいっもに、いっもいっも、いっもっに～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hum-hum-hu~m\nPotato‚ together‚ potato potato‚ together~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15.2999996821,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-living-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 200.0003179000007
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ski_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_ski_01_05-ski002.m4a",
      "text": "ハッ！　あれは理想の妹と名高い、すみれちゃん……！\nすみません、ちょっといいですかっ！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah! That's Sumire-chan‚ famous for being the ideal sister…!\nExcuse me‚ do you have a moment!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.7341505368,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-living-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5033.3333351
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ski_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_ski_01_05-smr002.m4a",
      "text": "沙季さん？　いきなりどうしたんですか？\nわぁっ！？　び、びっくりしたぁ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Saki-san? What’s wrong all of a sudden?\nWhoa!? Y-You scared me…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ski_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_ski_01_05-smr003.m4a",
      "text": "なるほど。今度出演するCMで、妹役をやるんですね\nうんうん、ミニドラマでも役作りは大切だと思います",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see. You’re playing the younger sister in your next CM.\nMm-hmm‚ character study is important even for a mini-drama.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 37.6113547007,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ski_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_ski_01_05-ski003.m4a",
      "text": "はい。私もそう思って役作りをしているんですが\n改めて考えると、どう演じていいか悩んでしまって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes. I thought so too and have been practicing‚ but\nthinking about it again‚ I'm worried about how to perform.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 48.4733500797,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ski_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_ski_01_05-ski004.m4a",
      "text": "私は幼い頃から、お姉ちゃんとしてしっかりしなきゃ\nってずっと思ってきたので、想像がつきにくいというか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Since I was little‚ I've always felt I had to be a reliable sister‚\nso it’s hard for me to imagine being on the other side…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 58.2066834131,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ski_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_ski_01_05-smr004.m4a",
      "text": "そっかぁ、千紗さんのお姉ちゃんですもんね\n逆の立場って、なかなかピンとこないのかも",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That makes sense‚ since you’re Chisa-san's older sister.\nIt might be hard to grasp the opposite role.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 67.1733521143,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ski_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_ski_01_05-smr005.m4a",
      "text": "なら一度、演じてみませんか？　私がお姉ちゃんの役を\nやるので、沙季さんは妹の役をお願いします！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Then‚ shall we try acting? I'll be the older sister‚\nand you can play the younger sister‚ Saki-san!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 76.7936435063,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ski_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_ski_01_05-ski005.m4a",
      "text": "なるほど、試しに即興で演じてみる、ということですね\n実際にやってみることで分かることもありそうです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see‚ like an improvised acting exercise.\nI might learn something by actually doing it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 85.1436888694,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ski_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_ski_01_05-ski006.m4a",
      "text": "それでは…………………………\nほんぎゃあ……！　ほんぎゃあ……！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Alright then………………\nWahhh…! Wahhh…!!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 94.8770222027,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ski_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_ski_01_05-smr006.m4a",
      "text": "え……沙季、さん……？　え……\nえぇぇぇ！？　なんで赤ちゃんをやってるんですか！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh… Saki-san…? Huh…\nWhaaaat!? Why are you acting like a baby!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 101.2436903953,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ski_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_ski_01_05-ski007.m4a",
      "text": "妹として誕生したところから、順番にやった方が\nお互いイメージしやすいんじゃないかと思って",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I thought starting from birth as a younger sister\nwould make it easier for both of us to visualize.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 109.010923926,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ski_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_ski_01_05-smr007.m4a",
      "text": "だからって赤ちゃんからやらなくていいですよ！？\nほ、ほら、もう少し成長した姿を想像して……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But you don't have to start from a baby!?\nL-Look‚ imagine a slightly more grown-up version…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 115.9442572593,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ski_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_ski_01_05-ski008.m4a",
      "text": "なるほど……では……。すみれお姉ちゃ～ん\nえへへ、大好き～。ぎゅ～～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see… Then… Big sis Sumire~\nEhehe‚ I love you~ Squeeze~~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 125.0350734392,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-03.m4a",
          "delay": 11344.556650199991
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ski_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_ski_01_05-smr008.m4a",
      "text": "わぁ！？　沙季さん……じゃなくて、さ、沙季？\nもぉ、急に抱きつかないの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Whoa!? Saki-san… I mean‚ S-Saki?\nGeez‚ don't just hug me out of the blue.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 139.0017401058,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ski_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_ski_01_05-smr009.m4a",
      "text": "び、びっくりしたけど、なんかいいかも……\n甘えてもらえるのって、お姉さんになった気分……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I-I was surprised‚ but this actually feels nice…\nBeing relied on really makes me feel like a big sister…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 147.4717858313,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ski_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_ski_01_05-ski009.m4a",
      "text": "――それから五年後\nちょっと何見てんの？　じろじろ見てんじゃねーよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――Five years later\nWhat are you looking at? Don't stare at me!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 155.7446717897,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ski_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_ski_01_05-smr010.m4a",
      "text": "……って、五年の間に何があったの沙季！？\n明らかに悪い友達が出来てるよね！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Wait‚ what happened in those five years‚ Saki!?\nYou definitely fell in with a bad crowd‚ didn't you!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 163.4113384563,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ski_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_ski_01_05-ski010.m4a",
      "text": "あ、これは反抗期を表現してみました\nCMで演じるのはハタチの大学生なので、後六年ですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ I was expressing the rebellious phase of adolescence.\nThe role in the CM is a 20-year-old student‚ so 6 years to go.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 170.4163954733,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ski_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_ski_01_05-smr011.m4a",
      "text": "や、やっぱり幼少期から順番にやっていきたいんだ……\nでも入り込んでる分、演技力は凄いかも……あはは……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You really want to do this in order from childhood…\nBut since you're so immersed‚ your acting might be amazing… ahaha…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 180.48306214,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}